X. Combat related military pay if the pay is the result of deployment to or service in a combat zone and was not received immediately prior to serving in combat zone.

Y. Guaranteed Basic Income is a program where individuals receive direct cash payments on a regular basis if they meet the eligibility criteria for that program. Income from this program is exempt when any funding comes from a private source.

Z. Universal Basic Income is any payments that is funded solely with private funds or mixture of private and public funds will be excluded income.

